---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Rajshahi Blog - Sessions & Presentations">
  <main>
    <h1>Sessions & Presentations</h1>
    <p>A collection of past talks, presentations, and video discussions. These are moments where thoughts were shared, ideas explored, and knowledge exchanged, often in a contemplative and reflective manner.</p>

    <section class="sessions-list">
      <h2>Presentations</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            The Art of Digital Minimalism <span class="session-date">(October 2023)</span>
          </a>
          <p class="session-description">A talk on decluttering digital spaces for enhanced focus and peace of mind.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Astro & Content Collections: Building a Quiet Blog <span class="session-date">(July 2023)</span>
          </a>
          <p class="session-description">Demonstrating how to leverage Astro's content features for a simple, elegant blog.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Videos & Discussions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Reflections on Open Source Philosophy <span class="session-date">(April 2023)</span>
          </a>
          <p class="session-description">A video discussion on the collaborative and communal aspects of open-source development.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  .sessions-list ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .sessions-list li {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .sessions-list li a {
    color: var(--heading-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .sessions-list li a:hover {
    color: var(--link-hover-color);
  }
  .session-date {
    color: var(--date-color);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
  }
  .session-description {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
